Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,avatars and the great spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time have we got left
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and what slide are we on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes? Let me see how far we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we? What number are we on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at... What number is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Avatars and great
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I better hustle along. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether lollygag or
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,hustle. Try to look at my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because we could spend the whole day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about any one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just grab one. We could spend the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,day. Here's the Rig Veda that we mentioned before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 7.05.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A Course in Miracles is well known.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've written that the workbook
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The textbook is at 550
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,because it gets into
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a little duality in the workbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These are very
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,ancient. Apocrypha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and Bodhidharma Zen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,teachings at almost 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bhagavad Gita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,910. See, these came out of the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,ancient Vedas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Book of Kells
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,at 570.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody familiar with the Book of Kells?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The illuminated manuscript done
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,by the Irish priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to Dublin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to see the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Book of Kells.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time I was there many years ago, there was quite a few
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of them. Now they have exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,one copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day they turn one page.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, they've made
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,copies that they illuminate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,on the wall. But a lot of those
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,illuminated manuscripts calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,well over 700. I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,we went to see it and when we started
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to look at this one on the wall, we all started to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at it made you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That particular illustration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated over 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Book of Mormon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at 405.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cloud of Annoying,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely well known, mystical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,705.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystical always calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest in all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's religions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dead Sea Scrolls
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,are historically exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritually, only at
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,260. The Dhammapada
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,at 840.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Diamond Sutra
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,at 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Doctrine and Covenant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pearl of Great Christ at
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,455 of Mormonism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Genesis in the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lomza Bible at 660.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gnostic Bible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gospels are 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gospels of St. Luke,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Thomas are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,all in the high 600s.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Holy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bible of the Sikhs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,505.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heart Sutra,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,780. Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that Nico
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,chants here is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what is that? Seven and something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lotus Sutra, especially
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's chanted in Sanskrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so the Heart Sutra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The teachings of Wang Po
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,require
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we got time for the explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. See, Wang Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,if you read, Wang Po was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,one of my favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wang Po, the Zen teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of Wang Po calibrates at 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And he taught
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the pathway of negation, to negate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality of the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,linear, to let go of any
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,attachment to the linear, because the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is transitory, an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you practice it assiduously,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you will end up in the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,850
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I spoke of the void, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in the current book that just came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I speak about it again
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in some length in the future, in the book
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that came out next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Duosional non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The pathway of negation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,will take you to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,850 is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Many Buddhist
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,practitioners have made
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the error of thinking the void is the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,reality. It is not. And Arhat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The void is nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In as much as the ultimate reality
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is allness, nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothingness is an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The negation of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,linearity, what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there is that God
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as love has been negated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By negating love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see love in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego's idea of love
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as an attachment, then
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the pathway of negation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,would take you to invalidate love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you invalidate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,love and let go of all attachment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to all linearity, you will end up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in the void. The void
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is not a thousand. The void is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,850. Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell you one thing about the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It is profoundly impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is very easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To conclude, that this is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate state taught
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,by the Buddha of nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Voidness, no-thingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing means no-thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It means non-linear. No-thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean non-existent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, I went into
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the void again. I started in this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime. I came in in the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then day three,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it was shockingly, went back and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,came back into existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you exist, but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you had a physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,exist, comes the terror of non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the trauma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of realizing you exist, then the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,fear of non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because at 850, you haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,transcended that duality of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,existence versus non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you've got to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,come back. If all you've got, the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,farthest you ever got was 850, when you come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you come back at 850 and start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,From nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is profoundly love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,again, back into
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the void. The void is infinitely
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinitely impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's infinite. It's eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It is extremely profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Except that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as an adolescent in the snowbank,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd experienced the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,as profound love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's its most major
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lack of thingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no thingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But the radiance of love was like
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,just profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The radiance of love
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,shone forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the void,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was, by comparison,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,sterile. Profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Unending. No beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Had to back out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because love is a quality of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity. If you negate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you just negated divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a local teacher that I know extremely well
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,made that error.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that love was an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people all end up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,flat. Into the flat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,nothingness. Devoid of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, love
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is a quality of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huang Po, when he wrote,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he did,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he did write it, but at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,he taught, it was quoted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,aphorisms of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen teachings of Huang Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, he calibrated it at 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huang Po discovered the error.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And he went past 850, and by the time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,he died, he was at 960.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But between the time he was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,at 850 and the time he was at 960,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't write anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Which I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,natural state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Natural state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So he never said anything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,after he reached that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's trackable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was 960
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,when he left the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So he discovered the error himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they do the good karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart Sutra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huang Po's teachings. The Kabbalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,605.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see how the Kabbalah is being brought down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with some kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,popularization. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The King James Bible, we read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have quite a section on the Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to spend a lot of time this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about both the Bible and the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Koran. The King James
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bible calibrates much less
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,than the Lompsa Bible,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which is from the Aramaic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lompsa Bible,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,minus the Old Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and minus the Book of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Revelations. The Book of Revelations calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,around 70. It was somebody's lower astral
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,hallucination. Calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,at 80. So the worst thing that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,happened in the Council of Nicaea was the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,conclusion of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Revelations by John. John
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated at 70, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Book of Revelations calibrated at 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That brought down the calibration of the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bible. That's
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,why Christianity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,was very high until
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,after the Council of Nicaea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already spoken about that, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,About the lower astral vision
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of John. It's very common.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people in Sedona have had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They have. Some well-known
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,leaders who crashed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your etheric body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,astral realms,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,people think they're possessed by
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,extraterrestrials, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, what happens is they
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,experience that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They experience that in a lower astral realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when they come back in the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it was very real. They experimented
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with my eyes and took my heart out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and put it back in, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're convincing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because subjectively, experientially,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what they did experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All these people of, what do they call it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,extraterrestrial possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No. In an altered state,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they went to a lower astral realm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what went on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they came back in the body and reported it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They were in a lower astral
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,realm, reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One was a well-known teacher in Sedona
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,who did that, plus negating love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the Bible then
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,included that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lao Tzu's teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,are extremely high. The Lotus Sutra,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,which we're going to hear this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,These are great books
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of Judaism.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we've already spoken about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the highest version
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of the New Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Lamsa edition
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Aramaic
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with the deletion of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the Book of Revelations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, it comes up to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,something like 880 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nicene Creed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher than I expected it to, 895.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Psalms from the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lamsa Bible are 650.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ramayana, the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of Omar Khayyam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent my soul into the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,afterlife, some
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,message
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And my soul returned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to me and said, I myself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,am heaven and hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,famous quote at
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,about 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rig Veda we've already spoken of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Talmud is extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibetan Book of the Dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,575. The Torah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The concept of the Trinity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,at 945.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, you see the Trinity in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddhism, I mean in Hinduism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Arama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Upanishads are extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,970.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Vedanta,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the Vedas,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,these are all extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Zohar, which is mystical
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Judaism,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,at 905.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the time we have for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying to cover all this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll do more this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll have time for
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,questions and answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm looking forward to having
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,a small group that meets
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,just one evening every other month
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is it'll be spontaneously just
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,question and interaction, discussion of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the implications of much of what we've
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And so therefore, all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,have, when they're
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,contextualized correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see how innocuous
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you can see that your chances of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,are zero if you follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not like we're knocking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we're knocking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,all that we teach then
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is contextualized
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of having
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment as one's ultimate goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything we say is from the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Many things are swell,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but not if you're seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go and get your aura read,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you can do the beads,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you can do the cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you can do all the Swami stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're on your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if your goal is enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a great deterrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can blow many, many, many lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,following all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of us here have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us here have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all checked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then something
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,within our soul said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,okay, you've checked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So our intention then
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is these are for the people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,who've been around,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we've all been around in many lifetimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,plus we've often done it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have often swooped in together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,this whole group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been together a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've checked it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've gratified
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,our childish curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,about the runes and the stones
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and sacred readings and ooh la la ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The hearts and the flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The slick looking gurus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,someday I'm going to come in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in my real guru outfit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to do smoke
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and various tricks that I've learned
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,over many a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned a lot of tricks
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,over many lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make things materialize
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and dematerialize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we'll be back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,at what time for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,2 o'clock. We'll resume at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was going to start
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the afternoon with the problematic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,hermeneutics of relativistic epistemology.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Comical and yet critical
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to our existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I did leave some
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,reprints of moral relativism
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a printout from
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the Philadelphia Trumpet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because moral relativism
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,as the Pope said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the primary problem of society
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in which wars and things
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,are the automatic fallout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why try to attack war
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when the cause is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,relativistic moralism
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I agree with the current Pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Pope
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd he do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,without me? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The new book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an error on page 342.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All books have errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I buy a book, commercial book
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and it never has errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Every book we do is read by
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,32 people 32 times
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's always a misprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, humility. Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonia, the chief editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of us have read it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,about 43 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,On page 342, the reason it's important
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is because usually it's just
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a typo, but this changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It says
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, your calibrated level
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness, your spiritual destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,your karmic destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is set by intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it says, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like setting the compass on the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and every little wave that tips you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,this way or that way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,does not change
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,your ultimate destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The word do not was left out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It says don't fret over
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,every little annoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've picked peace, page 342.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It says somewhere on the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,second paragraph I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we forgot do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've set your compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've decided on enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time you get annoyed with something
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,or a little guilt with something
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean you've fallen off the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not change
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,your overall compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The compass is changed by a spiritual decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,not by every little wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So do not was left out of there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't want to obsess
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the compulsive people going home
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and beating themselves up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because the word do not,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:21:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll think, he said, oh you are off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I say about making mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was 342.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, do not was left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We always say a little something
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,about this subject here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done this one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it a little differently this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come around this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the top picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the bottom picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the bottom picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to repeat what we've done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the top picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the bottom picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the bottom picture
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and think the sound ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.27,0:22:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Think the sound ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,skeptics think you're faking kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.74,0:22:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't fake it because
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.74,0:22:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all non-verbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks at that, goes strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.74,0:22:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks at that, goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I say make a sound in your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and she goes strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very simple thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I wanted to say about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we'll go to the next...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were we before lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to move fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Other teachings, schools and traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now when we published the book
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we had to decide whether we want to please everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So throughout the book it warns you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're not writing this to please everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what the numbers came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.49,0:23:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The numbers that came up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is all that we're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The hundredth monkey phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is not just illusory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.06,0:23:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out at 2.05.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody familiar with the hundredth monkey phenomena?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The monkeys on one island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:24:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a bunch of islands
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with monkeys on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.05,0:24:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The missionaries or somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.70,0:24:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,taught the monkeys on one island
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to wash their potatoes before they ate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.70,0:24:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The monkeys would take it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and wash the potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.04,0:24:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Within I forget a decade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.04,0:24:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the monkeys on other islands completely separated
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.04,0:24:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,began to wash their potatoes before they ate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.04,0:24:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like picked up in the collective.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.04,0:24:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the hundredth monkey phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you go to clear things in yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.21,0:24:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point in feeling badly
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.21,0:24:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because the collective unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.21,0:24:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you've already picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.21,0:24:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of the hundredth monkey phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.21,0:24:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.07,0:24:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're intelligent monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've already picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.58,0:24:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,through the hundredth monkey phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.58,0:24:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what Jung called the collective unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.58,0:24:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.58,0:24:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,very intense very advanced spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.58,0:24:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you become dismayed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.58,0:24:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that stuff is coming up in you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.58,0:25:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that you cannot recall in your personal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.58,0:25:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because beyond a certain level
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.58,0:25:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you're picking it up from the collective
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.58,0:25:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,belief system of
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the unconscious belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.65,0:25:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.03,0:25:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what does this say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.03,0:25:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Gnosticism is 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.03,0:25:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Atheism is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.03,0:25:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Atheism is arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.03,0:25:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It means I know, I know there is no God.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.03,0:25:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you can see the arrogance of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.03,0:25:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Gnosticism is honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.03,0:25:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have myself
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.09,0:25:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unable to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.09,0:25:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity is a reality or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.09,0:25:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.39,0:25:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself went through very intense
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.11,0:25:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,first I started out
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.11,0:25:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,as an atheist and then I became more
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.11,0:25:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,sophisticated and became an agnostic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.11,0:25:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I got straight A in theology
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.11,0:25:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time I was an atheist agnostic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.44,0:25:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-creationism
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.44,0:25:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.99,0:25:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-evolutionism
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.99,0:25:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,150.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.66,0:26:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Archangel channelers usually calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.66,0:26:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,about 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.65,0:26:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Astrology is problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.65,0:26:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on what kind of astrology you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.65,0:26:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out higher than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.72,0:26:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,210 and then some
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.72,0:26:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,variations of it are 405.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.25,0:26:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to do with causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.25,0:26:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we mentioned this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.25,0:26:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.48,0:26:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words a planetary
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.48,0:26:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,constellation is not causing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.48,0:26:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,things to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.48,0:26:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that they're both
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.22,0:26:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,energized in such a way
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.22,0:26:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're in synchronicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.22,0:26:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And when Mercury's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.22,0:26:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,going over your backyard it's very likely
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.22,0:26:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,your bunions will hurt more than
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.22,0:26:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when Neptune is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.22,0:26:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.67,0:26:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,your soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.95,0:26:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Biofeedback
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.95,0:26:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,202.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.95,0:26:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bodywork 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.95,0:26:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well the body and the planet is at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.95,0:26:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The earth is at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.95,0:27:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is at 200. That's like neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.95,0:27:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither good nor bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.95,0:27:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither good nor bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.55,0:27:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither the body nor the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.55,0:27:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So the body is the product of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.55,0:27:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of the physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.97,0:27:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,From ashes you dust your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.97,0:27:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and from dust you return.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.20,0:27:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,From 200 you go to the body
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.20,0:27:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and 200 goes back to 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.48,0:27:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.48,0:27:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bodywork 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.48,0:27:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The concept of codependency
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.75,0:27:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,at 190
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.33,0:27:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is less than 200 because
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.33,0:27:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it confuses love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.72,0:27:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Many things are done out of love
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.72,0:27:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it sort of eliminates
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.72,0:27:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,love from the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.81,0:27:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime you serve other ones
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.81,0:27:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not necessarily codependency.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.81,0:27:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.81,0:27:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So codependency
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.81,0:27:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,has a certain validity
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.00,0:27:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's used correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.14,0:27:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Creationism is at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.14,0:27:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystals at 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.14,0:28:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Druids at 450.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.43,0:28:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ekankar 230.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.58,0:28:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Enneagrams
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.03,0:28:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,390.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.03,0:28:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Est.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.20,0:28:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How many here did Est?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.20,0:28:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a few of us did, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.23,0:28:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.39,0:28:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And Est just didn't allow you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.39,0:28:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to blame anything out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.39,0:28:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were late
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.42,0:28:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because you decided to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.42,0:28:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't because the streetcar got in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.42,0:28:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.51,0:28:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,for your own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.51,0:28:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That would have
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.51,0:28:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,quite a positive effect in today's world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.51,0:28:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,would it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.51,0:28:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In which cause is always
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.51,0:28:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,put out there as blame
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.57,0:28:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of just accepting
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.57,0:28:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that it was your own error.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.57,0:28:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethical culture
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.71,0:28:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,at 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.71,0:28:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,During the time I was an agnostic and an atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.71,0:28:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked a lot of these things out
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.71,0:28:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,like ethical culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.71,0:28:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ways of reaching truth that avoided
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.71,0:28:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the terminology of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.71,0:29:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Falun Gong
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.02,0:29:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,105. Doesn't do too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.02,0:29:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Feng Shui can be anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.02,0:29:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,from 185 to 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.02,0:29:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Like astrology it depends on
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.02,0:29:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,what it's about
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.05,0:29:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and why it's used.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.05,0:29:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire walking is at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.41,0:29:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Freemasonry at 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.36,0:29:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Freethinker at 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.36,0:29:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the founders of the constitution
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.36,0:29:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,were freethinkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.36,0:29:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They were deists and theists
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.55,0:29:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but they were freethinkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.55,0:29:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Freethinkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.55,0:29:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why our constitution
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.88,0:29:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is really quite liberal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.35,0:29:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the congress not establish
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.35,0:29:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a religion
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.42,0:29:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,nor prohibit the free exercise
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.42,0:29:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which the enemies of religion
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.42,0:29:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,always manage to delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.42,0:29:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the lack of integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.42,0:29:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why people in that political position
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.42,0:29:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see that's dishonest.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.42,0:29:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The phrase is neither establish nor prohibit
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.42,0:29:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the free exercise thereof.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.42,0:29:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So purposely to chop off
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.74,0:30:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,this half means to be
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.74,0:30:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,dishonest.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.74,0:30:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dishonest puts you below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.34,0:30:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright so that's easy to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.34,0:30:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fundamentalism 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.73,0:30:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot what fundamentalism is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.73,0:30:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatha yoga
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.07,0:30:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is good stuff at 260.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.07,0:30:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Holotropic breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.07,0:30:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,at 202.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.07,0:30:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huna is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.52,0:30:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.52,0:30:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,123.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.59,0:30:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,260.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.13,0:30:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The I Ching in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.13,0:30:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The keys of Enoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.13,0:30:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,160.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.13,0:30:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirlian photography
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.13,0:30:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,came out at 160
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.13,0:30:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a surprise to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.25,0:30:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got Kirlian photographs
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.25,0:30:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,at my fingertips and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.25,0:30:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all into it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.44,0:30:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd do all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.44,0:30:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd chant and all that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.44,0:30:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'd go and see our fingertips again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.44,0:30:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really an attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.44,0:31:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.92,0:31:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Knights Templar, what does that say?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.92,0:31:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,400?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.33,0:31:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's of interest
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.33,0:31:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,recently because
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.33,0:31:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Da Vinci Code
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.33,0:31:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the focus on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.33,0:31:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Kung Fu
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.40,0:31:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and seeing metaphysics.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.40,0:31:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Numerology
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.50,0:31:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,at 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Qigong, 240.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.50,0:31:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebirthing, that's quite an exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.50,0:31:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,250.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.03,0:31:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiki in the 300s.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.03,0:31:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rolfing, it says
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.03,0:31:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.03,0:31:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So things that are strictly physical
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.03,0:31:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,don't get too far beyond the 200s.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.00,0:31:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosicrucians
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.00,0:31:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at 405.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.00,0:31:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul midwifery
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.00,0:31:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,at 240.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.13,0:31:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Superstition at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.13,0:31:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.13,0:31:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it incorporates
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.35,0:31:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is within the collective.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.93,0:31:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Telepathy at 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.93,0:32:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It means it's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.08,0:32:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And Theosophy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.08,0:32:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which has a great tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.16,0:32:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Universalist Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.38,0:32:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And the White Brotherhood
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.85,0:32:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,at 560
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.85,0:32:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Celestial Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.15,0:32:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,White Magic, 203.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.40,0:32:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Den, 275.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.40,0:32:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody got any questions
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.40,0:32:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,about any of those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.40,0:32:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's relatively clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Brotherhood
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.31,0:32:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is really a Celestial Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.31,0:32:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.57,0:32:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to do the White Brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're over 560.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.86,0:32:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,570.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.00,0:32:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconditional Love
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.00,0:32:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is a Celestial Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.27,0:32:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The work, let's see,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.27,0:32:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the translator of transmissions
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.27,0:32:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,from that realm was
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.82,0:32:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice Bailey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.36,0:32:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.36,0:32:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the book that I think
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.36,0:33:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is useful
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.36,0:33:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one on Glamour.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.59,0:33:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What you find attractive out there
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.59,0:33:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you think the attractiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.59,0:33:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.59,0:33:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What it points out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.59,0:33:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you project
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.59,0:33:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that specialness onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.59,0:33:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're craving
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.00,0:33:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what you think is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.00,0:33:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's out there is just you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.00,0:33:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you put out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.54,0:33:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.41,0:33:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The white meaning purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.41,0:33:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.41,0:33:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's a great place to go
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.64,0:33:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if you leave and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.73,0:33:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,invite it to join the White Brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.73,0:33:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a great honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.73,0:33:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It means they have
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.55,0:33:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,detained themselves from going further
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.55,0:33:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.55,0:33:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.75,0:33:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.10,0:33:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,are sufficiently advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.10,0:33:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if they wanted they could go on
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.10,0:33:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but they wouldn't then
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.10,0:34:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,be involved in human affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.10,0:34:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So for the sake of humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.10,0:34:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they detain their own
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.61,0:34:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,these are things that all calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.61,0:34:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.61,0:34:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them get so much publicity
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.61,0:34:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and they've come up in classes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.61,0:34:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so many times
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.61,0:34:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that we finally did them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.61,0:34:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Al-Qaeda as we said this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.61,0:34:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.61,0:34:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Atheist Movement is at 190.
