Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.84,0:51:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,come here Toronto
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.07,0:51:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.07,0:51:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to put on a lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.07,0:51:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.07,0:51:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the work happen
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.07,0:51:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is just the visible ones
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.07,0:51:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there are others here too
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.07,0:51:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that don't show up
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.07,0:51:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,on photographic film
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.07,0:51:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if you know what I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.07,0:51:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,who's going to introduce them
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.76,0:51:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.28,0:51:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this is Tom I know he's Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.28,0:51:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because it says right there it's Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.28,0:51:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Susie you going to introduce everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.28,0:51:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,well I don't have a mic
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.28,0:51:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,here's Gabe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.28,0:51:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,give her a mic
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.23,0:51:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,start right there from the end
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.23,0:51:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll go right across
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.23,0:52:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,hi Gail Edwards Decker
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.23,0:52:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert Decker
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.75,0:52:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dale
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.53,0:52:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lou
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.21,0:52:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Joe
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.21,0:52:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lonnie
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.09,0:52:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.17,0:52:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.42,0:52:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.42,0:52:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Louris
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.48,0:52:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Laura
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.11,0:52:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,some of them teach study groups online
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.11,0:52:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,other of them contribute in other ways
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.11,0:52:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to help us put on lectures for you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.11,0:52:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we just want all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.11,0:52:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to acknowledge them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.11,0:52:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and without them we wouldn't be able to do
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.11,0:52:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,these wonderful lectures for you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.11,0:52:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.11,0:52:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and Doc
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.11,0:52:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.34,0:53:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.36,0:53:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to put on a lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.36,0:53:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the people
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.36,0:53:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that we hardly ever get a chance to acknowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.36,0:53:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in public
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.36,0:53:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,ok now we have Miko Champ for you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.36,0:53:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we will have a short break
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.36,0:53:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and we will resume
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.36,0:53:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,back here
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.36,0:53:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,at 3 o'clock
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.63,0:53:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,remember to
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.63,0:53:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,line up on this side
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.63,0:53:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want your books signed
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.63,0:53:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or this side if you want your books signed
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.63,0:53:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if you have any questions
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.63,0:53:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,this side for only books only
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.63,0:53:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.63,0:53:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there will be quite a few today
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.63,0:53:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,since the book just came out
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.63,0:53:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so we will see you in a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.63,0:53:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and Miko let me get you set up
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.25,1:00:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that Jesus
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.92,1:00:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,brought salvation to mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.92,1:00:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,salvation yes
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.96,1:00:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would like to know
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.96,1:00:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,salvation from what
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.96,1:01:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and by which means
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.96,1:01:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,by which means did he do so?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.19,1:01:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,man in and of himself
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.46,1:01:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is incapable of transcending
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.46,1:01:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,his own limitations
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.46,1:01:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.11,1:01:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,beneficence of the savior
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.11,1:01:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,who is your
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.94,1:01:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,who speaks for you at the right hand
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.94,1:01:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,at the father
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.09,1:01:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,salvation
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.59,1:01:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,man left to himself
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.76,1:01:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is incapable of it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.94,1:01:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the very structure of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.94,1:01:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,also you forget
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.26,1:01:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got an inheritance
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.26,1:01:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic inheritance of the collective unconscious
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.26,1:01:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind all together
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.26,1:01:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so the chance of you on your own
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.26,1:01:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,reaching salvation
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.53,1:01:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment or whatever you want to call it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.53,1:01:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is very very limited
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.15,1:01:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and he did so by
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.15,1:02:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha taught enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.15,1:02:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a different thing
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.07,1:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,salvation somebody speaks for you
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.21,1:02:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment you transcend all the levels
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.21,1:02:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for which you would need a savior
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.82,1:02:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.30,1:02:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what do I do with this wonderful box?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.03,1:02:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,just sign it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.03,1:02:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,who is this about?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.96,1:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like a box of weenies
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.96,1:02:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,or something
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.96,1:02:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,hello
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.96,1:02:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,just by us being here
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.96,1:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,do we protect ourselves from
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.96,1:02:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual downfall?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.09,1:02:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,just by being where?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.61,1:02:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.61,1:02:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in a spiritual class?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.92,1:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,yes of course
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.92,1:02:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't be here if you weren't in there
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.92,1:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting in spiritual integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.23,1:02:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so therefore your enlightenment is already in tegris
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.23,1:02:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who is dedicated to spiritual truth
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.28,1:02:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is already way above 200
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.28,1:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200 you got to worry about
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.28,1:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,what's going to happen to you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.07,1:03:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200 you got worries
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.07,1:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,over 200
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.96,1:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.96,1:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,hi
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.34,1:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been mentioning unconscious programming
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.34,1:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot the last few months
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.34,1:03:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,like with your osteoporosis
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.34,1:03:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with what?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.34,1:03:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,your osteoporosis
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.34,1:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you pick up from the collective
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.34,1:03:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything that we should be doing
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.34,1:03:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in particular to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.34,1:03:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,offset that besides the course of miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.34,1:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is there like a specific
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.34,1:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,something we should hold in mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.34,1:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as you become alert to being programmed
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.34,1:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you can tell when you're being programmed
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.34,1:03:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and refuse it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.55,1:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but unwittingly one gets programmed
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.98,1:03:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think as I demonstrated
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.98,1:03:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,pig nose
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.40,1:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,pig nose
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.40,1:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,alright now forget that
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.03,1:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you've already been programmed with the nose of a pig
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.03,1:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.03,1:04:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,pig nose
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.03,1:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't have
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.03,1:04:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody said
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.03,1:04:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,now I want you to decide whether or not
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.03,1:04:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to include this in your memory bank
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.03,1:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it happened without your permission
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.40,1:04:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore that's the intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.40,1:04:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the intrinsic innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.67,1:04:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can be programmed
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.67,1:04:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,against your own will
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.67,1:04:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so we just accept it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.67,1:04:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or we
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.67,1:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,say we're only subject to what we hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.69,1:04:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that's correct
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.69,1:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.69,1:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're going to be clearing things
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.69,1:04:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I bring this up is because
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.69,1:04:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to be clearing things
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.50,1:04:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that you in your personal recollection
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.50,1:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,don't remember
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.88,1:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet you obviously picked it up someplace
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.88,1:04:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're manifesting it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.88,1:04:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought osteoporosis
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.88,1:04:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is for little bent over ladies
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.88,1:04:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.09,1:04:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and like specifically
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.09,1:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for calibrating things
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.09,1:05:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're doing calibrations
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.09,1:05:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,does the unconscious beliefs
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.09,1:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,come into play when we're
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.09,1:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,doing calibrations
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.73,1:05:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,no because you're bypassing it
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.73,1:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.73,1:05:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,research calibrates at 600
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.73,1:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so the 600
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.92,1:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is the interface between the linear
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.92,1:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the non-linear
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.73,1:05:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever you're believing doesn't influence it
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.73,1:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so we don't have to specifically
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.73,1:05:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,say
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.73,1:05:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to clear anything before we calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.73,1:05:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so generally speaking
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.73,1:05:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.80,1:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't get a
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.80,1:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,response that you think is
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.80,1:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriate you could go
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.80,1:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,ha ha ha ha ha ha ha
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.80,1:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,clear yourself and then
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.80,1:05:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,recalibrate it
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.96,1:05:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,also it's best
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.96,1:05:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask do I have permission to calibrate this
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.96,1:05:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as you'll see during
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.96,1:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the lectures sometimes we get
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.96,1:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,something really tacky
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.23,1:05:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll ask do we have permission and it says no
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.23,1:06:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ok good
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.44,1:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.44,1:06:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,good questions
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.19,1:06:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.28,1:06:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,chinks or the traps
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.28,1:06:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,about what? about the traps on the pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.28,1:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,say it real slow
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.32,1:06:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the traps on the pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.32,1:06:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,traps on the pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.57,1:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,traps on the pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.57,1:06:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yes
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.57,1:06:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for example when you're in this state
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.57,1:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,when everybody falls in love with you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.57,1:06:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or vice versa
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.57,1:06:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,on every level there's
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.57,1:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the traps
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.92,1:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,having known a couple of people that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.92,1:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,crashed very badly
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.11,1:06:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what their specific
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.11,1:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,problem was
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.19,1:06:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,one of them I wrote up already in the lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.19,1:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,confused personal love
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.19,1:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,with divine love
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.86,1:06:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is a serious mistake
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.86,1:06:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because personal love is an attachment
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.86,1:06:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you then cancel
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.86,1:07:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality of love itself
