Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.93,1:15:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,this is weakening
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.93,1:15:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew a guy that couldn't even
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.93,1:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,make Mrs. cats happy
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.93,1:15:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so seriously there's no acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.93,1:15:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or anything that can help
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.93,1:15:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.93,1:15:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that's true
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.23,1:15:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,65 happy cats and she's complaining
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.23,1:15:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,if I can keep one cat happy
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.93,1:15:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm doing good
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.93,1:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,hi Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.72,1:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.01,1:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,can you speak up here in your presence
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.01,1:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.01,1:15:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you in May
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.01,1:15:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've changed my life
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.01,1:16:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.01,1:16:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it had a good effect
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.01,1:16:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.01,1:16:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a graduate psychotherapy program and
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.01,1:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I graduate in what
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.01,1:16:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,psychotherapy
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.01,1:16:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I find myself now
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.01,1:16:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,after being exposed to your work
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.01,1:16:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling frustrated
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.01,1:16:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,or finding myself judgmental
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.01,1:16:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of people in my program
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.01,1:16:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that haven't been exposed to your teachings
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.01,1:16:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making them wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.01,1:16:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because they haven't been exposed to your work
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.10,1:16:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering how to work with that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.10,1:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a hard one to come across
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.10,1:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,as you evolve spiritually
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.10,1:16:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the spleen of the spiritual warrior comes up
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.10,1:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you become indignant at the evil in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.10,1:16:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the blatant lying
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.10,1:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what the constitution says
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.77,1:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,do not establish a religion
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.77,1:16:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,nor prohibit the free practice thereof
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.77,1:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so where does
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.77,1:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the anti-Christmas
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.77,1:16:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,BS come from
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.39,1:16:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.39,1:16:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard not to be indignant about it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.39,1:16:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual pride comes up
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.39,1:16:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so anyway
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.39,1:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to accept
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.39,1:17:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,what Socrates said
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.39,1:17:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that everyone is doing what they think
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.39,1:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is the right thing to do
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.85,1:17:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.61,1:17:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.61,1:17:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Michael Newdow calibrates at 205 or something
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.61,1:17:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,not 80, not 90
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.92,1:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he keeps coming up
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.92,1:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Supreme Court
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.92,1:17:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,hoping to knock God out of here someplace
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.92,1:17:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Charisma is God
