Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.01,1:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so if he's over 200 he may be mistaken
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.01,1:17:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's doing what he feels
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.30,1:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,called upon to do
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.30,1:17:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's part of the evolution of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.30,1:17:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to hear such voices
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.30,1:17:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.32,1:18:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.81,1:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,my question
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.05,1:18:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has to do about grief
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.11,1:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a dear
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.11,1:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,friend of mine, a priest who was really influential
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.11,1:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in my life in college passed away
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.11,1:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a priest friend of yours passed away?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.11,1:18:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.94,1:18:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you know going through your work
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.94,1:18:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and contemplating non-attachment
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.94,1:18:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything
