Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.94,1:18:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really feel anything
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.94,1:18:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we did a practice counseling session
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.94,1:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at my school and I was just overwhelmed
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.10,1:18:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and weeping as I held him in mine
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.10,1:18:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's definitely not a depressed
