Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.19,1:18:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just an overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.19,1:18:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,grief
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.19,1:18:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah and kind of a couple with gratitude
