Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.46,1:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as you progress
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.46,1:19:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words often I even think of you Susan
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.46,1:19:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when you pass
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.46,1:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.46,1:19:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that's just my question
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.52,1:19:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how to handle grief
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.68,1:19:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.68,1:19:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how to handle grief
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.68,1:19:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see
