Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.02,1:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.48,1:19:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.97,1:19:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not the easiest thing
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.88,1:19:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more emotional
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.88,1:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's such a common experience
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.88,1:19:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all of mankind's experience grief
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.88,1:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all of mankind's
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.88,1:20:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,experience grief
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.68,1:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you mentioned before
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.68,1:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it was all non-verbal the feeling of it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.68,1:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you mentioned grief can be many lifetimes of grief
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.68,1:20:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or something
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.68,1:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,yes every negativity you pull up
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.68,1:20:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,has been accumulated throughout all of
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.68,1:20:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your human
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.84,1:20:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,incarnations
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.84,1:20:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's the collective
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.93,1:20:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,grief that you're letting go of
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.93,1:20:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've collected all these lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.93,1:20:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,see many times we didn't process
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.31,1:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,out a thing we just suppressed it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.96,1:20:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it comes up again later
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.96,1:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but now there's more of it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.96,1:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because you've suppressed it so often
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.96,1:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,just allow it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.96,1:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to flow and don't resist it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.96,1:20:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,don't call it grief don't call it anything
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.96,1:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something coming up
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.96,1:20:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and you stop resisting it whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.96,1:20:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you just let go resisting it
