Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.30,1:20:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.46,1:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,releasing all the accumulated
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.46,1:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of that
