Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.18,1:24:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,burning you up
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.61,1:24:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you jumped into the fire yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.61,1:24:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,can I have a picture
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.26,1:24:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of both of you
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.26,1:24:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.80,1:25:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just going to say
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.10,1:25:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,smile for the birdies you collected
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.39,1:25:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,how would you describe
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.39,1:25:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,compassion
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.76,1:25:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,compassion is the inclusion
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.76,1:25:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of the equality of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.76,1:25:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so that instead of
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.68,1:25:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,identifying with an isolated
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.68,1:25:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,individual
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.42,1:25:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that you identify
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.42,1:25:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with the unfolding of life
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.42,1:25:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,itself
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.72,1:25:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,compassion is
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.85,1:25:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,intuiting the sacredness of all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.85,1:25:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the divinity of all
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.27,1:25:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,creation
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.34,1:25:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.02,1:25:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the sacredness of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.02,1:25:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.02,1:25:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it stands out
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.02,1:25:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,when you reach a certain level
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.02,1:26:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it stands out from everything
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.06,1:26:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes it difficult to function
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.06,1:26:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for a while frankly
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.39,1:26:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have trouble with this concept
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.39,1:26:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of the lack of
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.39,1:26:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship between cause and effect
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.39,1:26:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly in the case of
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.39,1:26:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a pool where one billiard ball hits another one
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.39,1:26:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems like there is a clear
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.39,1:26:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Newtonian design
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.39,1:26:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can see that in human beings
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.39,1:26:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in human relations
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.39,1:26:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it difficult to accept
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.39,1:26:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in a pure physical sense
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.46,1:26:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,can you help me to
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.46,1:26:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,get over that hurdle
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.77,1:26:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you mean in the physical
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.77,1:26:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or the human
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.77,1:26:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,one billiard ball hitting another
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.77,1:26:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a clear cause and effect
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.77,1:26:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,no there is no clear cause and effect
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.77,1:26:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you are projecting that belief system
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.84,1:26:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,onto it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.84,1:26:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,well that is probably true
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.56,1:26:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,how do I get over that
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.56,1:26:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,oh ok
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.56,1:26:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,got any hints
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.56,1:27:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.61,1:27:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what you see is emergence
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.72,1:27:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of potentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.72,1:27:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,into actuality
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.90,1:27:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,when the conditions are appropriate
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.90,1:27:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.13,1:27:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,half unfolded rose
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.19,1:27:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is anything going to cause it
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.35,1:27:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to unfold to a full rose
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.35,1:27:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't cause it
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.31,1:27:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what you do
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.31,1:27:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it has within it the potential
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.31,1:27:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,under appropriate conditions
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.31,1:27:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,warmth, sun and light
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.31,1:27:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,each thing is unfolding
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.31,1:27:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.31,1:27:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the potentiality of this can
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.31,1:27:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it is going to be tipped up in the air
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.31,1:27:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,or I can just dump it on the ground
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.07,1:27:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and say it is bad for you
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.07,1:28:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.07,1:28:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so there is an infinite number of choices
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.07,1:28:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so local conditions
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.07,1:28:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,are going to influence
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.07,1:28:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.07,1:28:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of its emergence into an actuality
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.15,1:28:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,if you sort of meditate on emergence
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.15,1:28:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you will see everything
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.15,1:28:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is the emergence of a potentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.15,1:28:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,your being up on the stage
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.15,1:28:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is not caused by anything
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.15,1:28:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you held it as a value
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.15,1:28:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and my being here was held as a value
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.43,1:28:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,consequently
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.43,1:28:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we emerged in the scene
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.43,1:28:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you know at the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.43,1:28:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.43,1:28:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing caused me to come here
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.43,1:28:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing caused you to be here
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.43,1:28:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing caused you to ask a question
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.43,1:28:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing caused me to answer it
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.92,1:28:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,well the intention then
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.92,1:28:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.05,1:28:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the upcoming classes
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.05,1:28:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that we are going to do
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.05,1:28:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,on the alternate months
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.05,1:28:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is you know a dream I have
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.05,1:28:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.05,1:29:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with no exchanges of money
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.05,1:29:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have to hire a place
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.05,1:29:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can just have free exchange
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.05,1:29:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of dialogue
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.05,1:29:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought that is what is ideal
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.05,1:29:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you can walk around barefoot
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.05,1:29:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and just dialogue with people
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.05,1:29:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to rent a hall
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.31,1:29:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or anything
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.31,1:29:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and so in the modern world though
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.31,1:29:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you got to have insurance
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.31,1:29:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and you got to have a staff
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.31,1:29:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and you got big maintenance
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.31,1:29:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and clean up afterwards
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.31,1:29:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and parking places
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.64,1:29:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is very big
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.64,1:29:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so you hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.64,1:29:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what you hold in mind tends to manifest
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.64,1:29:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe you can see it that way
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.64,1:29:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what you hold in mind tends to manifest
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.64,1:29:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so having held that in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.64,1:29:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ideal setting
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.64,1:29:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what is happening is
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.64,1:29:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,currently is about to emerge
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.64,1:29:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so it is the emergence
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.73,1:29:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of potentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.46,1:30:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what he means
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.46,1:30:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he has been scientifically
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.55,1:30:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,educated
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.55,1:30:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in science
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.55,1:30:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two questions
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.55,1:30:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the harmonic conversions
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.64,1:30:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.64,1:30:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.64,1:30:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.64,1:30:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.64,1:30:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,oh I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.64,1:30:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of humanity went up
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.64,1:30:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,oh the timing of it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.98,1:30:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was concordant
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.98,1:30:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the harmonic concordance
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.98,1:30:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at that time
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.98,1:30:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't caused by it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.94,1:30:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't caused by it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.94,1:30:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so what caused it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.94,1:30:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing caused it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.07,1:30:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,did you just listen to the last gentleman
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.07,1:30:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,ok
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.61,1:30:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,very quickly
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.61,1:30:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,are you related
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.61,1:31:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the potentiality existed within mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.61,1:31:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,ok
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.61,1:31:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and it happened at the most propitious time
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.61,1:31:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,all the people praying
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.10,1:31:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,all the people forgiving
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.10,1:31:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,there was at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.10,1:31:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,back in the 80's
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.10,1:31:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.22,1:31:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever it was
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.22,1:31:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,people held hands all around the highways
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.22,1:31:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,people prayed all over the world
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.22,1:31:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.22,1:31:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the consciousness level of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.22,1:31:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,jumped as a result
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.47,1:31:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,do you have any suggestions
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.47,1:31:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,how to overcome the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.47,1:31:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to be special or overcome negativities
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.47,1:31:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.30,1:31:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,do the course of miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.30,1:31:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,ok
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.30,1:31:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it deals with specialness
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.97,1:31:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the downfalls
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.97,1:31:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of gurus
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.97,1:31:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is specialness
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.97,1:31:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,even the term guru
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.97,1:31:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.97,1:31:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in the book
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.97,1:31:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we had no one using the term
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.97,1:32:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,about the time of the Beatles
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.97,1:32:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the term guru fell
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.43,1:32:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,glamour, money
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.15,1:32:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.19,1:32:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the guy wants lots of followers
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.19,1:32:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you want lots of followers for
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.19,1:32:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't you got enough problems
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.28,1:32:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer the email now
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.96,1:32:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.10,1:32:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.13,1:32:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.02,1:32:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.19,1:32:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to get some help today
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.19,1:32:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with an issue I've been working on
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.19,1:32:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for the last year
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.19,1:32:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but I got a call at lunch time
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.19,1:32:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that made me request
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.19,1:32:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,if I could trade my question for a prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.19,1:32:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.52,1:32:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,stepson has been struggling
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.52,1:32:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,along his own
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.52,1:32:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic path as it is
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.52,1:33:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with addictions etc
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.52,1:33:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and last night
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.84,1:33:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,his father committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.84,1:33:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your stepson committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.84,1:33:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,no his father did
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.84,1:33:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the stepson's father
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.84,1:33:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.84,1:33:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was wondering if
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.84,1:33:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,now or at some time
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.84,1:33:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I also asked the people here
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.84,1:33:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if they could pray for
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.84,1:33:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,people why
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.86,1:33:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,one has a drug problem
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.86,1:33:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the stepson has a drug problem
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.86,1:33:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and his father committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.86,1:33:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so if we could have some kind of unity prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.86,1:33:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yes
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.86,1:33:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of prayer would you hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.02,1:33:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I would hold that
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.02,1:33:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Evan my stepson is
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.02,1:33:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,given strength
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.43,1:33:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue along his
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.43,1:33:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,path some strength
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.85,1:33:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what about his own karmic
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.88,1:33:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,option and choice
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.88,1:33:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want us to cheat him out of his karmic inheritance
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.88,1:33:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.88,1:33:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of his own he makes the decision
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.88,1:34:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,however we can create the field
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.88,1:34:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the likelihood of us choosing positive
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.88,1:34:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is supported by all of us collectively
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.88,1:34:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be good
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.88,1:34:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so let us all collectively hope for the best
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.88,1:34:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for the people that you mentioned
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.35,1:34:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's up to the will of God
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.35,1:34:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,up to the old lord
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.35,1:34:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the karmic inheritance
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.35,1:34:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the people
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.35,1:34:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and we apologize for interjecting
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.35,1:34:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,our volition
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.35,1:34:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to the matter which is probably not of our
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.35,1:34:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,concern
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.35,1:34:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we do appeal to thee
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.35,1:34:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for thy divine mercy
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.35,1:34:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen
